{"word":"G185 - ἀκέραιος - akéraios - ak-er'-ah-yos - Harmless","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀκέραιος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">akéraios</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ak-er'-ah-yos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Harmless</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"கபடற்ற, பேதை - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"unmixed, pure, as wine, metals, without admixture of evil, free from guile, innocent, simple"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1 - Α - A - al'-fah/1\">G1</a> (as a negative particle) and a presumed derivative of <a href=\"#/G2767 - κεράννυμι - keránnymi - ker-an'-noo-mee/2767\">G2767</a>; <i>unmixed</i>, that is, (figuratively) <i>innocent:</i> - harmless, simple.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}